---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "October 2023";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="bg-white pt-[120px] pb-24 px-6" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:6x0g76">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[300px_1fr] gap-12" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:pffnzo">
      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <aside class="hidden lg:block" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:xxwxbb">
        <div class="sticky top-[120px]" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:pffnzp">
          <h3 class="text-dark font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[12px] mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:sa922f">Compliance</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4 list-none p-0 m-0" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:compliance-nav">
            <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8du">
              <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-[#00A896] font-semibold text-[15px] transition-colors" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:tu2lda">Privacy Policy</a>
            </li>
            <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8dt">
              <a href="/terms-of-service" class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-[#00A896] text-[15px] transition-colors" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:tu2ld9">Terms of Service</a>
            </li>
            <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8ds">
              <a href="/regulatory-disclosures" class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-[#00A896] text-[15px] transition-colors" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:tu2ld8">Regulatory Disclosures</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="max-w-[800px]" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:pffnzq">
        <h1 class="text-dark text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:12kscw">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-12" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:y33jw4">Last Updated: January 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-10" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:pffnzr">
          <section data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:y5a2re">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:dlu4uu">1. Introduction and Scope</h2>
            <p class="text-foreground leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:y33jw5">
              SPVH Private Limited ("SPVH," "we," "us," or "our") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal, financial, and proprietary data. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, process, safeguard, and share information when you visit our website, apply for our investment programs (including "The First Cheque"), or engage with our ecosystem of business verticals. By accessing our platform or providing us with your information, you consent to the data practices described in this policy.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:y5a2rd">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:dlu4ut">2. Categories of Information Collected</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-foreground" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cat-info">
              <p class="leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:y33jx2">To effectively evaluate investments and manage capital, we collect specific categories of information:</p>
              <ul class="space-y-4 list-disc pl-5">
                <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8dr"><strong class="text-dark">Identity & Contact Data:</strong> Full name, email address, phone number, physical address, and professional profiles (such as your LinkedIn URL).</li>
                <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8dq"><strong class="text-dark">Financial & KYC Data:</strong> Information required for compliance and wealth management, which may include Permanent Account Number (PAN), Aadhaar details, bank account information, net worth declarations, and investment history.</li>
                <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8dp"><strong class="text-dark">Business & Proprietary Data:</strong> Information submitted during the funding evaluation process, including pitch decks, financial models, capitalization tables, intellectual property details, and strategic business plans.</li>
                <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8do"><strong class="text-dark">Technical Data:</strong> Internet Protocol (IP) address, browser type, operating system, and usage data collected via cookies when you navigate our platform.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:methods-col">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:methods-title">3. Methods of Data Collection</h2>
            <p class="text-foreground mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:y33jx3">We collect information through the following channels:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-foreground list-disc pl-5">
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8cz"><strong class="text-dark">Direct Interactions:</strong> When you fill out forms on our website (e.g., the "Access Program Deck" form), correspond with us via email, or execute physical/digital contracts.</li>
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:social-media"><strong class="text-dark">Social Media Platforms:</strong> Information such as images, communications, or public profile data when you interact with our official social media channels.</li>
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8cy"><strong class="text-dark">Third-Party Sources:</strong> Information obtained during our due diligence process from credit rating agencies, background verification providers, and public regulatory filings.</li>
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8cx"><strong class="text-dark">Automated Technologies:</strong> Through cookies and analytics tools that monitor platform performance and user engagement.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:y5a2rc">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:dlu4us">4. Purpose of Data Processing</h2>
            <p class="text-foreground mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:y33jx4">We strictly use your information for legitimate business and operational purposes:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-foreground list-disc pl-5">
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8cw"><strong class="text-dark">Investment Evaluation:</strong> To assess business models, process applications for our Ideapreneur, Solopreneur, Entrepreneur, and Familypreneur programs, and facilitate capital deployment.</li>
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8cv"><strong class="text-dark">Portfolio & Wealth Management:</strong> To manage alternative investment strategies, execute capital market transactions, and provide advisory services.</li>
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8cu"><strong class="text-dark">Regulatory Compliance:</strong> To adhere to Anti-Money Laundering (AML) laws, Know Your Customer (KYC) norms, and annual compliance reporting requirements mandated by regulatory bodies.</li>
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8ct"><strong class="text-dark">Communication:</strong> To send program updates, administrative notices, and respond to your direct inquiries.</li>
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:marketing-news"><strong class="text-dark">Marketing & Newsletters:</strong> To send periodic emails, newsletters, and information about investment topics you have agreed to receive.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:y5a2rb">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:dlu4ur">5. Information Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
            <p class="text-foreground mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:uvx640">We treat your data with strict confidentiality. We do not sell your data. We may share information under the following circumstances:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-foreground list-disc pl-5">
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8c7"><strong class="text-dark">Intra-Group Sharing:</strong> Data may be shared between SPVH Private Limited and its subsidiaries (Financial Services, Media, Hospitality, Automotive, Technology, Real Estate) to execute cross-vertical synergies and operational efficiency.</li>
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8c6"><strong class="text-dark">Trusted Service Providers:</strong> We may share data with secure third-party vendors, such as legal counsel, auditors, and cloud hosting providers, who are bound by strict non-disclosure agreements.</li>
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8c5"><strong class="text-dark">Legal & Regulatory Authorities:</strong> We will disclose information to statutory bodies (such as SEBI, RBI, or law enforcement) if legally mandated or to protect the rights and safety of the firm.</li>
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:acc-aggregator"><strong class="text-dark">Account Aggregator Ecosystem:</strong> Data may be shared through the Account Aggregator ecosystem or any similar consent artefact as and when notified by SEBI.</li>
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:logistics-payments"><strong class="text-dark">Logistics & Payment Intermediaries:</strong> Information may be shared with intermediaries such as couriers for correspondence and banking partners for Electronic Clearing Services (ECS) and NEFT payments.</li>
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8c4"><strong class="text-dark">Business Transfers:</strong> In the event of a merger, acquisition, or restructuring, user and business data may be transferred as part of the holding group's assets.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:y5a2ra">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:dlu4uq">6. Data Security and Retention</h2>
            <div class="space-y-6 text-foreground" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:security-retention">
              <div data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:pffnzq">
                <strong class="text-dark block mb-2">Security Measures:</strong>
                <p data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:uvx641">We implement institutional-grade technical and organizational safeguards, including secure servers, encryption protocols, and strict access controls, to protect your sensitive financial and business data against unauthorized access.</p>
              </div>
              <div data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:pffnzr">
                <strong class="text-dark block mb-2">Retention:</strong>
                <p data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:uvx642">We retain your information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy, or for the duration mandated by Indian financial and corporate compliance laws (which frequently require record preservation for a period of years post-transaction).</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:rights-choices">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:rights-title">7. User Rights and Choices</h2>
            <p class="text-foreground mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:uvx643">Subject to applicable laws, you hold the following rights regarding your data:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-foreground list-disc pl-5">
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8c3"><strong class="text-dark">Right to Access & Correct:</strong> You may request access to the personal data we hold about you and ask for corrections to any inaccuracies.</li>
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8c2"><strong class="text-dark">Right to Withdraw Consent:</strong> You may withdraw your consent for future data processing or opt out of specific communications.</li>
              <li data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:cuv8c1"><strong class="text-dark">Right to Erasure:</strong> You may request the deletion of your data, subject to our overriding legal or regulatory obligations to retain certain records.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:y5a2r9">
            <h2 class="text-dark text-2xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:dlu4up">8. Grievance Redressal</h2>
            <div class="text-foreground" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:grievance-content">
              <p class="mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:uvx644">If you have any questions, concerns, or complaints regarding this Privacy Policy or our data handling practices, please contact our Grievance Officer at:</p>
              <p class="font-bold mb-1" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:uvx645">Email: <a href="mailto:info@spvhgroup.com" class="text-[#00A896] hover:underline" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:tu2ld7">info@spvhgroup.com</a></p>
              <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:uvx646">Subject Line: Please use "Privacy Grievance" or "Data Protection Query" in your subject line to ensure prompt routing.</p>
              <p data-ps="src/pages/privacy-policy.astro:uvx647">We are committed to addressing your concerns promptly and thoroughly in accordance with applicable data protection regulations.</p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
